s. However, above the middle arch in the bridge, you&#x2019;ll also see a solid column that was priorly used as a prison! These days, you can visit these chambers for a small exhibition.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also visit: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/spain\/seville\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The beautiful city of Seville in Spain.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>The Best Viewpoints<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>There are four interesting viewpoints to admire the bridge from. Firstly, you can walk down a few stairs and follow a sand path for about 10 minutes for a stunning lower-angle viewpoint (<a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/ZRZS5erygcaZ1Frr6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">here is the location<\/a>). You&#x2019;ll also be able to spot the beautiful waterfall below the bridge from this spot. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103220\/ronda-spain-6.jpg\" alt=\"things to do ronda spain Puente Nuevo\"><\/noscript><img width=\"265\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do ronda spain Puente Nuevo\" class=\"wp-image-85554 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1503px) 100vw, 1503px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103220\/ronda-spain-6.jpg 1503w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/