utiful part of the town that offers impressive views over the surrounding landscape. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3.jpg\" alt=\"ronda Arco de Felipe V spain\"><\/noscript><img width=\"254\" height=\"338\" alt=\"ronda Arco de Felipe V spain\" class=\"wp-image-85557 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1444px) 100vw, 1444px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3.jpg 1444w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-451x600.jpg 451w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-609x810.jpg 609w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-254x338.jpg 254w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-123x163.jpg 123w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-135x180.jpg 135w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-578x768.jpg 578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-770x1024.jpg 770w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-812x1080.jpg 812w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-1083x1440.jpg 1083w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-300x399.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20103416\/ronda-spain-3-600x798.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\