     <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-9-plaza-de-toros-de-ronda\">9. Plaza de Toros de Ronda<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the reasons tourists visit Ronda is because it&#x2019;s home to the oldest stone bullring in all of Spain. Bullfighting plays a big part in the history of Andalusia, and by visiting Plaza de Toros, you get a small glimpse of what this sport meant for the town back in the day. Not only is it a grand building, but it&#x2019;s an excellent place to learn more about the Real Maestranza De Caballer&#xED;a, the oldest order of horsemanship. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"307\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-86072 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-800x545.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-1080x736.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-450x307.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-264x180.jpg 264w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-768x524.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-1024x698.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-1440x982.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-600x409.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-150x102.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/21154848\/ronda-spain-30.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>However, even though this sport was important historically, we recommend that you don&#x2019;t watch a bullfight as this is a bad example of wildlife tourism.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Things to know about Wildlife Tourism<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Did you know:<\/strong> although this bullring might not be the largest in the world (5000 seats), it does have the largest <em>Rueda<\/em> (the circle of sand in the middle), which has a diameter of 66 meters!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do ronda spain travel guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do ronda spain travel guide\" class=\"wp-image-85883 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20153111\/ronda-spain-11.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-10-puerta-de-almocabar-iglesia-del-espiritu-santo\">10. Puerta de Almoc&#xE1;bar &amp; Iglesia del Esp&#xED;ritu Santo<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enter Ronda through one of the 13th-century town gates: Puerta de Almocabar. Located on the southern side of the town, these walls and the gate are one of the most impressive remains of history in Ronda.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The name comes from the Moorish word &#x2018;Al Maqabir&#x2019;, meaning cemetery. Traditionally, Moorish cemeteries were built outside of the town walls. Because of this, the gate was one of the main entrances to the town and led through to what is currently known as Iglesia del Espiritu Santo (the Church of the Holy Spirit).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-ronda\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Ronda.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17.jpg\" alt=\"things to do ronda spain Iglesia del Esp&#xED;ritu Santo\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do ronda spain Iglesia del Esp&#xED;ritu Santo\" class=\"wp-image-85879 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/20152127\/ronda-spain-17-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourh